GIT

VIDEO: 25

- Introduction to GIT
    - Git is Global Integration Tool)
    - It is a open source
    - Any Cloud Provider can use
    - 2 types of GIT
        * DVS (Distributed Version Control)
        * CVS (CVS (Centeralized Version Control)
    - Git Installation Process
    - Staging Area, working area
    - Git Global Configurations
        - git config --global.username "your-name"      # to Configure username into git
        - gir config --global.email "email-id"          # to configure email into git
    - git init      # To intialise git into working directory
    - git status    # to check the files tracked/untracked
    - git add .     # to add files from working directory to staging area
    - git commit -m ""      # to add files staging area to local repository  
    - git push origin main  # to push the changes from local respository to remote

